<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Team Invitation</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            color: #333; 
            max-width: 600px; 
            margin: 0 auto; 
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header { 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); 
            color: white; 
            padding: 30px; 
            text-align: center; 
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .content { 
            background: #f9f9f9; 
            padding: 30px; 
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
        .invitation-details {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }
        .accept-button { 
            display: inline-block; 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white !important; 
            padding: 15px 40px; 
            text-decoration: none !important; 
            border-radius: 25px; 
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
        }
        .accept-button:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5a6fd8 0%, #6a4c93 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .cta-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7ff 0%, #e8f4fd 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #e0e7ff;
        }
        .token-info {
            background: #e8f4fd;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
        .footer { 
            text-align: center; 
            margin-top: 30px; 
            font-size: 12px; 
            color: #666;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">Flow Space</div>
        <h1>You're Invited to Join a Team!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello!</p>
        
        <p>You've been invited to join the <strong>{{teamName}}</strong> team on Flow Space.</p>
        
        <div class="invitation-details">
            <h3>Team: {{teamName}}</h3>
            {{#if teamDescription}}
            <p><strong>Description:</strong> {{teamDescription}}</p>
            {{/if}}
            <p><strong>Role:</strong> {{role}}</p>
            <p><strong>Invited by:</strong> {{inviterName}} ({{inviterEmail}})</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-section">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #4c51bf;">Ready to Join?</h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; color: #666;">Click the button below to accept your invitation instantly!</p>
            
            <a href="{{acceptUrl}}" class="accept-button" style="color: white !important; text-decoration: none !important;">
                ðŸš€ Join {{teamName}} Team
            </a>
            
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #888; margin-top: 15px;">
                You'll be redirected to the team dashboard after accepting
            </p>
        </div>

        <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;">

        <h4>Alternative Methods:</h4>

        <p><strong>Option 1:</strong> Use the API directly</p>
        <div class="token-info">
            <strong>Endpoint:</strong> POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/teams/accept-invite<br>
            <strong>Headers:</strong> Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN<br>
            <strong>Body:</strong> {"token": "{{token}}"}
        </div>

        <p><strong>Option 2:</strong> Manual token entry in the application</p>
        <div class="token-info">
            <strong>Invitation Token:</strong><br>
            {{token}}
        </div>

        <p><strong>Important:</strong> This invitation will expire on {{expirationDate}}.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This invitation was sent by Flow Space team management system.</p>
            <p>If you didn't expect this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>